  <brief_title>Assessment of the Effect of PAP on Energy and Vitality in Mild OSA Patients: The Merge Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of the Effect of Positive Airway Pressure on Energy and Vitality in Mild Obstructive Sleep Apnea Patients: The Merge Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
